body:
This PR enables Firewood to export metrics so that clients such as Coreth can aggregate those metrics into its own.

## How
Splits the Firewood API into the following:

```go
// Start recorder
func StartMetrics()

// Start recorder and exporter
func StartMetricsWithExporter()

// Gather latest metrics
func GatherMetrics() (string, error)
```

`GatherMetrics()` is used by to create a custom Prometheus gatherer that can used by Coreth's Multigatherer.

## Testing

Extended the existing metrics test to account for `Gatherer`.
